text: Ðis is full ger, twelf monþas fulle and endlufan dagas and six tida, þæt is ðonne ðreo hund daga and fif and sixtig daga and feorðan dæl dæges, þæt syndon six tida.

Þæs bið twa and fifti wucena, and eahta þusend tida and seouan hund and sixti, hund eahtatig ðusenda hwila and six hund, ða man hateþ minuta, and seouan þusenda and six hund, þonne bið ðæs eac þara beorhtan hwila ðreo hund ðusenda, and fifti ðusenda, fif hund and twentig, ðonne bið þæs fif and þrittig þusenda pricla and feowortig.
On anre æfenneahtlicre tide beoð feower punctas, ten minuta, fiftene partes, feowortig momenta, be sumra manna tale.
